165
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,680
Cigarettes for sale!

166
00:06:17,280 --> 00:06:18,940
Sir, buy a pack of cigarettes.

167
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:20,760
The most common people on the pier are

168
00:06:20,760 --> 00:06:22,120
