174
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:32,080
Look.

175
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:33,720
Those are the runners

176
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:35,000
and collectors of letters.

177
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,680
You can see parallel traders

178
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:38,680
