187
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:58,400
Why do I see them transporting local specialties?

188
00:06:58,560 --> 00:06:59,440
Actually, our remittance agency

189
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:00,970
has many ways to make money.

190
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:02,840
Besides sending and receiving letters,

191
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:04,240
We will also operate rice shops,

192
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:06,500
warehouses, spice factories, and so on.

193
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:08,520
Look.

194
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:10,640
For the few months

195
00:07:10,640 --> 00:07:11,680
