196
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:12,360
our remittance agency

197
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:14,020
will take the collected funds

198
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,080
and put them into time deposits

199
00:07:15,080 --> 00:07:15,960
or loan them out

200
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:16,970
to earn a profit.

201
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:19,120
Meanwhile, before the ship sets sail,

202
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:19,840
we convert the funds

203
00:07:19,840 --> 00:07:21,680
into local specialty goods.

204
00:07:21,960 --> 00:07:23,640
Like Malayan rice,

205
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:25,890
spices, betel nuts, pepper, and so on.

206
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:26,480
This way,

207
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:28,340
after shipping them to Quanzhou,

208
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:30,760
