209
00:07:30,880 --> 00:07:31,800
Then, after deducting

210
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,280
the remittances for the families,

211
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:33,800
we can still

212
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:35,000
earn another profit.

213
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:36,920
So, when heading south

214
00:07:36,960 --> 00:07:38,120
back to Malaya,

215
00:07:38,159 --> 00:07:39,820
bringing Minnan specialties

216
00:07:39,880 --> 00:07:40,520
back there

217
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:41,560
