219
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:43,770
Exactly.

220
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,840
Come, let's go take a look over there.

221
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:47,200
Okay.

222
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:55,680
I don't care

223
