234
00:08:18,840 --> 00:08:20,240
As expected of a scholar,

235
00:08:20,400 --> 00:08:21,660
that's a good summary.

236
00:08:24,880 --> 00:08:25,760
Sending remittances!

237
00:08:25,760 --> 00:08:26,600
If you haven't sent your remittance yet,

238
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,760
