269
00:09:14,920 --> 00:09:17,580
You understand the Qiaopi business right away.

270
00:09:23,920 --> 00:09:24,920
Brother Mingshu.

271
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:26,250
Jiadong,

272
00:09:26,400 --> 00:09:27,130
